name: MIS NSR1926 Ethnicity report
description:
This report list physical attributes of all prisoners at an establishment selected at runtime. The report contains input controls which allows you to choose which information you see on the report. For information on how to use input controls, please see the 070 - Hints and Tips folder in Managment Information Reporting (MIS).
V00.00.01 Last Modified: 07/08/18

dataset.name: MIS load
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT DISTINCT BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.BUSINESS_DATE FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE (BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.LOAD_ID = (SELECT MAX(LOAD_ID) FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE NOT LOAD_END_DATETIME IS NULL))), dataset_ AS (SELECT BUSINESS_DATE FROM dataset_base_)
